::Prowl::

Prowl's eyes look over Iron Raptor's figure as she crosses her legs, sliding 
down from her head as she looks up, her body displayed very nicely in the 
pose. He blinks as she asks him something, too engrosed in looking at her to 
be really paying attention. Prowl blinks again, trying to figure out what she 
had said.

"Huh? Oh. You can send Ramulus," he says, walking toward the table and 
sitting down near Iron Raptor. He wasn't sure if she was mad at him for his 
comment or not, so he didn't make any further move toward her, "He can deal 
with Dinobot's attitude, and he's a good scout. He'll find them."
